NOON RADIO HEADLINES - MAY 20 . These are the main headlines of the news reported by Radio Latvia at noon on Tuesday . Reuters has not verified these reports and cannot vouch for their accuracy . - President Gunitis Ulmanis meets parliament factions today to dicuss the slow pace of non - citizen naturalisation . - LNNK dicusses possible candidates to the defence post , following sacking of the previous minister Andrejs Krastinsh amid a fuel purchase scandal . - Teachers will decide on what steps to take if their demand for pay increases are not met . - Expolat exhibition takes place in Russia , Novgorod with some 30 companies participating . A similar event is planned in November in Kaliningrad . - - Riga Newsroom , + 371 721 5240 
